      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant should be a student.\n1. The applicant should be from a [De-Notified](https://samarth.mp.gov.in/Public/Pages/TribesDetail?ID=2),[ Nomadic, or Semi-Nomadic](https://samarth.mp.gov.in/Public/Pages/TribesDetail?ID=1) Community.\n_*The applicant should not need to apply again for renewal while continuing in classes of the same rate (e.g., classes 1 to 5)._\n_*The applicant should be eligible for the scholarship even if they fail one academic year._\n",
